bombay sapphire is a brand of gin owned by bacardi   that was first launched in 1987 by idv.   in 1997 diageo sold the brand to bacardi.http://www.grovesandwhitnall.co.uk/gj - distillers-warrington/ its name originates from gin 's popularity in india during the british raj and the sapphire in question is the star of bombay on display at the smithsonian institution .

for pourer : bombay sapphire , with queen victoria on the label , is a british brand of this liquor

